Gym subscription, private medical care, daily fresh fruits and snacks in the office;
Cultural card on your birthday for books, theatre, cinema, opera and similar;
Quarterly team activities (e.g.: team dinners, team buildings, office events such as Halloween celebration, Christmas party etc.);
