Unlimited access to Samsung’s learning platform
Access to in-class trainings and various events/ conferences;
Subscription to Bookster library;
Family & Living
25 days of vacation per year;
Referral bonuses for new hires recommended by you.
Hybrid work (2 days/ week working from home);
